title: Russia cracks down on dissenting media, blocks Facebook - The Associated Press - en Español
content: Russia cracks down on dissenting media, blocks Facebook  The Associated Press - en EspañolView Full Coverage on Google News
description: DUSSELDORF, Germany (AP) — Russian President Vladimir Putin on Friday intensified a crackdown on media outlets and individuals who fail to hew to the Kremlin line on Russia's war in Ukraine , blocking Facebook and Twitter and signing into law a bill that criminalizes the intentional spreading of what Moscow deems to be “fake” reports.
